Objective

The primary objective of the study was to assess whether DAR-0100A treatment at low (Treatment_group = B in associated data) or high dose (Treatment_group = C in associated data) compared to placebo (Treatment_group = A in associated data) is able to improve memory as measured by the mem_comp rating.
Researchers were specifically interested in:

  • the treatment effects at day 5, 19, and 90 and
  • whether the treatment effects differed over time
